Source: apt-mirror
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Debian/Ubuntu Maintainers <debian-apt-mirror@lists.debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), python3, python3-aiohttp, xdelta3
Standards-Version: 4.0.0
Homepage: https://apt-mirror.github.io/
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/radawson/apt-mirror
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/radawson/apt-mirror.git

Package: apt-mirror
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, python3-aiohttp, xdelta3, ${misc:Depends}
Description: APT repository mirroring tool (async Python version)
 A tool for mirroring APT repositories with async support for improved
 performance. Features include:
  * Async downloads using aiohttp
  * Diff serving capability to reduce bandwidth
  * Better error handling and progress reporting
  * Improved performance for large mirrors
  * Compatible with existing mirror.list configuration format

